=Description=


ACTUS will provide all the necessary services to the community call spread. Services we offer include a survey of local resources and needs, call the model design, IT systems deployment and call management services. ACTUS is South Korea's first specialized institution for providing systematic services for the community currency. We are committed to the mission to enrich the community through the dissemination and education of the community currency.

ACTUS is to support sustainable economic activities, social development, public organizations that use community currency as a tool to reach the ecological balance, businesses, financial institutions, NGOs and citizens. We are developing research expertise across government policy, IT development, and design a payment transaction platform, execution and operations management to work legislation for local calls. The ACTUS cooperatives pursue social change through the development of innovative tools and consulting to maximize the positive impact of the community currency.


